Oauth2 server based on nodeJS.

Very partial and incomplete implementation at the moment. 
Tested with nodeJS v0.3.0.

To get / update the submodules:
  git submodule update --init --recursive

To run the tests (need nodetk bins on the path):
  nodetests src/tests

To Generate the mustache templates (for web app):
  make update_js_templates

To update it (skiping i18n stuff):
  make skip

